intro: This is a list of the National Register of Historic Places listings in McLean County, Kentucky. It is intended to be a complete list of the properties on the National Register of Historic Places in McLean County, Kentucky, United States. The locations of National Register properties for which the latitude and longitude coordinates are included below, may be seen in a map. There are 9 properties listed on the National Register in the county, of which 6 are part of a National Historic Landmark spread across multiple counties.
